text: Sawkat Ali Bhuiyan is a Bangladesh Nationalist Party politician and the former Member of Parliament of Tangail-3. ==Career== Bhuiyan was elected to parliament from Tangail-3 as a Bangladesh Nationalist Party candidate in 1979. ==References== Category:Bangladesh Nationalist Party politicians Category:Living people Category:2nd Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
title: Sawkat Ali Bhuiyan
